    • Method Detail

      • resolvePlaceholders

        public java.lang.String resolvePlaceholders(java.lang.String description,
                                            T testdata)
        Resolves any placeholder thats enclosed by ENCLOSE_START and ENCLOSE_END.
        Parameters:
        description - The String which should be checked for placeholders.
        testdata - The instance of which the placeholders are a field or method of.
        Returns:
        A String where all placeholders are resolved if a field or method like that is found.
        If none is found, the placeholder is inserted again.
